# HEALTHYLIFESTYLEWEBSITE
1.Project Title

Healthy Lifestyle Website 
using HTML, CSS & JavaScript

2.Project Description

This project is a single-page dynamic website designed to promote a healthy lifestyle. It includes sections like Home, Diet, Fitness, and Contact, all integrated into one file and controlled using JavaScript.

3.The website provides:

*Basic health tips
*Diet guidance with images
*Fitness exercises with progress tracking
*BMI calculator for users
*Contact form with validation

"JavaScript is used to make the website interactive and dynamic, simulating a multi-page website experience."

⚙️ Installation Instructions
Create a folder (e.g., HealthyWebsite)

Save your code as:
index.html

4.Add required images:
diet-plan.jpg
balanced-diet.jpg
protein-food.jpg
fitness1.jpg
fitness2.jpg
fitness3.jpg
Open index.html in any web browser (Chrome, Edge, etc.)

5.Usage:
Click Home / Diet / Fitness / Contact to navigate
Click “Show Tip” to display a health tip
View diet and fitness images
Track progress using animated bar
Enter height & weight to calculate BMI
Fill and submit the contact form

6.Features:
✅ Single-page website with multiple sections
✅ JavaScript-based navigation (no page reload)
✅ Interactive health tip button
✅ Image display for diet & fitness
✅ Animated progress bar
✅ BMI calculator
✅ Form validation
✅ Clean and responsive UI

